turning to the nearby blackjack as he did two blackjack bombers 
flew overhead in formation in the partly cloudy blue sky and the 
roar of their engines broke the silence of the largely deserted 
airfield 
carlucci inspected the underbelly of the fourengine blackjack 
and then climbed orange stairs into the open bomb bay doors and 
entered the cockpit he told reporters later he could not give 
technical details of the plane but compared it to the b1 bomber of 
the united states in that it can fly at low altitudes and carry 
heavy payloads 
